 of picking up right where you left off. There's an active community base and an active forum, and an at-times chatty lobby.Overall it is a very well-designed (and still being designed) game with great emersion, simple to learn, hard to master; lots of features and options and seems to have a robust future. Now let's all just get through 2017!"
